Hi Katharine, while we appreciate you taking the time to leave us a review, we do still offer celiac friendly options. We do work with many bakeries and other kitchens who do not process gluten and those items are pre-packaged and sealed. Our house menu does process gluten and is labelled as such. Thank you again and do reach out if we can help with anything else.
